+ Ingest Streaming Data\nwith Structured Streaming
++ spark.readStream
+++_ format("kafka"): message bus source
+++_ format("csv/json"): file-based stream
+++_ startingOffsets: latest / earliest
++ Schema Requirement
+++_ Explicit schema for file streams
+++_ inferSchema NOT supported in streaming
-- writeStream Options
---_ format("delta"): Delta Lake output
---_ outputMode: append / update / complete
---_ checkpointLocation: resume point
---_ toTable(): write to Unity Catalog table
-- Output Modes
---_ append: new rows only (ingestion default)
---_ update: changed rows (aggregations)
---_ complete: all rows rewritten (aggregations)
@endmindmap
